description: The Ornamental Plant Fact Skill gives information about particular plants such as the scientific name, the common name and family the plant belongs.  It also gives bloom time and describes the colors and shapes of the plant's flowers.
exampleInteractions: Alexa,Launch Plant Facts and tell me a fact
Alexa, Start Plant Facts and give me a fact
name: Plant Facts
shortDescription: Skill gives facts about Herbaceous Ornamental Plants
